Class UnderlinePageIndicator

  • java.lang.Object
    • View
      • com.viewpagerindicator.UnderlinePageIndicator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.support.v4.view.ViewPager.OnPageChangeListener, PageIndicator

    public class UnderlinePageIndicator
extends View
implements PageIndicator
    Draws a line for each page. The current page line is colored differently than the unselected page lines.
